    <tr>
      <td width='95%' align='left' valign='top' colspan=2><b><font color='#80000'>UHM........</font>, By Igahmus</b><br><br><p>&nbsp;Seems like most of the people posting here is whining about how mages have been had and that it sucks to use 500 mana....well, think about it for a second.<br>
<br>
1)  You can summon your epic weapon at will.<br>
2)  You get a very strong pet to assist you.<br>
3)  You can GIVE the pet the staff to use.<br>
4)  You can have a real tank from now on.  NO NEED TO SHOUT, &#34;Group in need of a TANK!&#34;<br>
5)  WHAT IS SO BAD ABOUT 500 mana?!!!!&nbsp;<br>
<br>
Once you reach level 50+, you will have about 1600-2200 mana!  SO WHAT IF YOU LOSE 1/4 OF YOUR MANA?!!  Just meditate like you have always done and things should be okay.<br>
<br>
Now the ONLY thing I can see mages griping about is the fact that you have to kill a GOD to get a blasted staff for the epic!!!<br>
<br>
THE HOURS SPENT CAMPING OUT THE STAVES OF ELEMENTS IS WHAT ANNOYS ME.<br>
<br>
</p>
